                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.522/63: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moore</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-07-04T18:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 4, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 4—1:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>64. My 62, July 3, 5 p.m. After further consideration we have decided it would be
                    preferable to withhold temporarily proposal of <hi rend="italic">modus
                        vivendi</hi> in order that we may urge element of time as reason for
                    proceeding at once with negotiations. If at the promised conference we find [it]
                    impracticable to proceed with negotiations, proposal will be maintained for <hi
                        rend="italic">modus vivendi.</hi>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
